          <title>
            <string language="en">Nucleophilic addition reaction of hydrogen cyanide with a carbonyl compound</string>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Nukleophile Hinzufügung Reaktion des

            <string language="x-mt-fr">Réaction nucléophile d'ajout de cyanure

            <string language="x-mt-pt">Reação nucleophilic da adição do cianido de

            <string language="x-mt-it">Reazione nucleofila dell'aggiunta dell'acido

            <string language="x-mt-el">Πυρηνόφιλη αντίδραση προσθηκών του υδροκυανίου με μια 
ένωση καρβονυλίων</string>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Reacción nucleophilic de la adición del cianuro
de hidrógeno con un compuesto de carbonyl</string>
          </title>
          <description>
            <string language="en">This is second of two illustrations showing the nucleophilic addition reaction of hydrogen cyanide with propanal forming 2-hydroxybutanenitrile. Here, the formation of the hydroxynitrile is shown.</string>
          </description>

          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Dieses liegt an zweiter Stelle bei zwei 
Abbildungen, welche die nukleophile Hinzufügung Reaktion des 
Wasserstoffcyanids mit dem Propanal zeigen, das 2-hydroxybutanenitrile
bildet. Hier wird die Anordnung vom hydroxynitrile gezeigt.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">C'est en second lieu de deux illustrations 
montrant la réaction nucléophile d'ajout du cyanure d'hydrogène 
avec du propanal formant 2-hydroxybutanenitrile. Ici, la 
formation du hydroxynitrile est montrée.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Isto é em segundo de duas ilustrações que 
mostram a reação nucleophilic da adição do cianido de hidrogênio 
com o propanal que dá forma a 2-hydroxybutanenitrile. Aqui, a 
formação do hydroxynitrile é mostrada.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Ciò è in secondo luogo di due illustrazioni che 
mostrano la reazione nucleofila dell'aggiunta dell'acido cianidrico 
con propanale che forma 2-hydroxybutanenitrile. Qui, la 
formazione del hydroxynitrile è indicata.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Αυτό είναι δεύτερη δύο απεικονίσεων που εμφανίζουν 
πυρηνόφιλη αντίδραση προσθηκών του υδροκυανίου με propanal τη 
διαμόρφωση 2- hydroxybutanenitrile. Εδώ, ο σχηματισμός του
hydroxynitrile εμφανίζεται.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Esto está en segundo lugar de dos ilustraciones 
que muestran la reacción nucleophilic de la adición del cianuro de 
hidrógeno con el propanal que forma 2-hydroxybutanenitrile. 
Aquí, la formación del hydroxynitrile se muestra.</string>
          </description>
